基本架構:
<!DOCTYPE html>    每個html文件上面都會寫
<html>
<head>
<title>Page Title</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>This is a Heading</h1>
<p>This is a paragraph.</p>

</body>
</html>
------------------------------------------------------------------
html  links -> 放網址 
<a href="https://www.w3xxxx">
------------------------------------------------------------------
html image -> 圖片 
<img src="xxx.jpg" alt="xxx.com" width = "104"  height="142">
(如果img無法顯現 alt可以幫助)
------------------------------------------------------------------
html button -> 按鈕
<button>  click me!   </button>
------------------------------------------------------------------
html 表列選項: 

<ul>                     --unordered html  無序
    <li> coffee </li>
    <li> tea    </li>
    <li> milk   </li>
</ul>

<ol>                     --ordered html  有序
    <li> coffee </li>
    <li> tea    </li>
    <li> milk   </li>
</ol>
------------------------------------------------------------------
html empty 空白換行  <br>  --後面不用加上</br>
 
<p> this is a <br> picture. </p>


